title: REBEL FC 1 Into the Lion's Den Main Event.mp4
description:
In the main event of the evening, Japanese superstar, Shooto icon, and samurai of the ring "Lion" Takeshi Inoue clashes with "Ruthless" Rob Lisita, a dynamic and entertaining brawler, who's desire to destroy his opponents in brutal fashion is second to none! This match is the essence of patience vs. violence!

Then, in the co-main event, Singapore's own Syafiq "The Slasher" Samad, brings his talents to his home country for the first time ever as he tries to stop "The Bomb," Gyo Pyung Hwang!
